                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt feature-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Secure</h3>
                    <p>Your data is protected with military-grade encryption and security measures.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-magic feature-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Intuitive Design</h3>
                    <p>Beautiful, user-friendly interface that makes navigation a breeze.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section id="screenshots" class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-5 fw-bold">App Screenshots</h2>
